<p>More precisely, I was wondering how many <code>std::pair</code> template constructor calls are made in the following code snippet: one (for a <code>std::pair&lt;const KeyType, ValueType&gt;</code>) or two (first one for a <code>std::pair&lt;KeyType, ValueType&gt;</code> by <code>make_pair</code> and then a second to <code>std::pair&lt;const KeyType, ValueType&gt;</code> by <code>insert</code>) ?</p>  <pre><code>std::map&lt;KeyType, ValueType&gt; m;  void addToMap(const KeyType&amp; key) {     ValueType val = someCalculation(key);     m.insert(std::make_pair(key, val)); } </code></pre>